184: // handleWatchEvent triggers reloading the cert and key file, and restarts a new watch if it's a Remove or Rename event.
185: // If one file is updated before the other, the loadCertKeyPair method will catch the mismatch and will not apply the
186: // change. When an event of the other file is received, it will trigger reloading the files again and the new content
187: // will be loaded and used.
188: func (c *DynamicCertKeyPairContent) handleWatchEvent(e fsnotify.Event, w *fsnotify.Watcher) error {
